With iteration and no math.log:

def bouncingBall(h, bounce, window):
    if h > 0 and 0 < bounce < 1 and window < h:
        passing = 1
        while h * bounce > window:
            passing += 2
            h *= bounce
        return passing
    else:
        return -1



stringa lettere separate
singola lettera
creo nuova lettera
ributto nella stringa